<div class="content means imeans" data-group="imeans" id="basicmean-wrapper">
    <h1><b class="title active" id="basicmean" data-group="imeans">基本释义</b><span class="seg"></span>
                <a href="javascript:watchit()" class="title disactive" data-for="detailmean">详细解释</a>
        <span class="seg"></span>
            </h1>
    <div class="tab-content">
    <p><strong>1. <a href="#ffdfggkj">好事[hǎoshì]</a></strong><strong>2. <a href="#jtqfqlan">好事[hàoshì]</a></strong></p><dl><dt><a name="#ffdfggkj">好事[hǎoshì]</a></dt><dd><ol><li><p> [Buddhist service]∶佛事或道场。特指为死事所做的超度仪式</p><p>扬起布幡作好事</p></li><li><p> [good deed]∶有益的事情</p><p>先驱者为国家做一件好事</p></li><li><p> [an act of charity]∶旧时指慈善的事情</p><p>给我做件好事吧,我的孩子</p></li></ol></dd></dl><dl><dt><a name="#jtqfqlan">好事[hàoshì]</a></dt><dd><ol><li><p>[meddlesome;officious] 喜欢多事。爱参与他人事务的</p></li></ol></dd></dl>
    </div>
